\pc \bd 74\bd*

\s Wachunga walipolinda
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Wachunga walipolinda Kucha nyama zao, Malaika mtukufu Alishuka kwao.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Wakacha sana wachunga, Akawatuliza, “Nawaletea habari Ya kuwapendeza.”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd ”Mji ule wa Daudi Leo amezawa \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd  ni \bd*\bd Kristo\bd*\bd  Bwana, Ilivyoandikwa”.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd ”Huyo mwana wa \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd  Ataonekana, Amelazwa kihorini Malazi hapana.”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Alipokwisha yanena Malaika hao Waliimba wimbo huu Usio na mwisho:\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd ”Enzi ni yake Munju juu, Na nchi salama, Kwa watu nao radhi kuu, Sasa na daima.”\bd*
